metadata.name: un vent d'hiver
metadata.description:
when the sun  
leaves behind  
whispers of autumn

for the room gets colder  
the pills stop working  
and my eyes grow darker

maybe i'll find  
a reason to wake up 
and heal my mind

or fall back into my habits  
just to bring back  
the feelings for a bit

to spiral into obsession  
and burn what's left  
to oblivion

so by the time its noon  
it all ends with this

one room
